trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection" /> class represents a connection to a DSML Gateway using SOAP over HTTP.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection" /> 클래스는 HTTP를 통한 SOAP를 사용하는 DSML 게이트웨이에 대한 연결을 나타냅니다.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of a <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection" /> class.
A <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlDirectoryIdentifier" /> object that specifies server for the connection.

The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.#ctor(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlDirectoryIdentifier)" /> constructor initializes a new instance of a <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection" /> class.
<paramref name="identifier" /> is null (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
Demand value: <see cref="F:System.Security.Permissions.SecurityAction.Demand" />
A <see cref="T:System.Uri" /> object that specifies server for the connection.
trans-unit.target: 연결에 대한 서버를 지정하는 <see cref="T:System.Uri" /> 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.#ctor(System.Uri)" /> constructor initializes a new instance of a <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection" /> class.
<paramref name="uri" /> is null (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
Demand value: <see cref="F:System.Security.Permissions.SecurityAction.Demand" />
A <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlDirectoryIdentifier" /> object that specifies server for the connection.
A <see cref="T:System.Net.NetworkCredential" /> object that contains the network credentials.
trans-unit.target: 네트워크 자격 증명을 포함하는 <see cref="T:System.Net.NetworkCredential" /> 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.#ctor(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlDirectoryIdentifier,System.Net.NetworkCredential)" /> constructor initializes a new instance of a <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection" /> class.
<paramref name="identifier" /> is null (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
Demand value: <see cref="F:System.Security.Permissions.SecurityAction.Demand" />
A <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlDirectoryIdentifier" /> object that specifies the server for the connection.
A <see cref="T:System.Net.NetworkCredential" /> object that contains the Network Credentials.
trans-unit.target: 네트워크 자격 증명을 포함하는 <see cref="T:System.Net.NetworkCredential" /> 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AuthType" /> value that specifies the authentication type to use for this connection.
trans-unit.target: 이 연결에 사용할 인증 형식을 지정하는 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AuthType" /> 값입니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.#ctor(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlDirectoryIdentifier,System.Net.NetworkCredential,System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AuthType)" /> constructor creates and initializes a new instance of a <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection" /> class using the specified identifier, network credentials, and authentication type.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.#ctor(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlDirectoryIdentifier,System.Net.NetworkCredential,System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AuthType)" /> 생성자는 지정된 식별자, 네트워크 자격 증명 및 인증 형식을 사용하여 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection" /> 클래스의 새 인스턴스를 만들고 초기화합니다.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="identifier" /> is a null reference (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="identifier" />이 null 참조(Visual Basic의 경우 <see langword="Nothing" />)인 경우

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="authType" /> value is not one of the DSML supported values.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="authType" /> 값이 DSML에서 지원하는 값 중 하나가 아닌 경우.

trans-unit.source: DSML only supports Anonymous, Ntlm, Basic, Negotiate and digest.
trans-unit.target: DSML에서는 익명, NTLM, 기본, 협상 및 다이제스트 인증만 지원합니다.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="authType" /> value is not one of the constants defined in the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AuthType" /> enumeration.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="authType" /> 값이 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AuthType" /> 열거형에 정의된 상수 중 하나가 아닌 경우

trans-unit.source: Demand value: <see cref="F:System.Security.Permissions.SecurityAction.Demand" />
An object derived from <see cref="T:System.IAsyncResult" /> that references the asynchronous request.
trans-unit.target: 비동기 요청을 참조하는 <see cref="T:System.IAsyncResult" />에서 파생된 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.Abort(System.IAsyncResult)" /> method cancels the asynchronous request.
<paramref name="asyncResult" /> is null (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).

<paramref name="asyncResult" /> was not returned by the corresponding call to <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.BeginSendRequest(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument,System.AsyncCallback,System.Object)" />.

The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.AuthType" /> property contains one of the values of <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AuthType" /> enumeration that specifies the authentication type.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.AuthType" /> 속성에는 인증 형식을 지정하는 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AuthType" /> 열거형 값 중 하나가 포함되어 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: One of the values of <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AuthType" /> enumeration that specifies the authentication type.
trans-unit.target: 인증 형식을 지정하는 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AuthType" /> 열거형 값 중 하나입니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument" /> object to send.
The <see cref="T:System.AsyncCallback" /> function.
An <see cref="T:System.Object" /> that contains the state data for this request.
trans-unit.target: 이 요청의 상태 데이터를 포함하는 <see cref="T:System.Object" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.BeginSendRequest(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument,System.AsyncCallback,System.Object)" /> method begins asynchronously sending the specified <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument" /> object to the server.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.BeginSendRequest(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument,System.AsyncCallback,System.Object)" /> 메서드는 지정된 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument" /> 개체를 서버에 비동기적으로 보내는 작업을 시작합니다.

trans-unit.source: An object derived from <see cref="T:System.IAsyncResult" /> that references the asynchronous send.
trans-unit.target: 비동기 보내기를 참조하는 <see cref="T:System.IAsyncResult" />에서 파생된 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="request" /> is null (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.BeginSession" /> method instructs the DSML server to start a new session.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.BeginSession" /> 메서드는 새 세션을 시작하도록 DSML 서버에 지시합니다.

trans-unit.source: The method will block while waiting for a response from the DSML server and will time out according to the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryConnection.Timeout%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 메서드가 DSML 서버 로부터 응답을 기다리는 동안 차단 되며에 따라 시간이 초과 됩니다는 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryConnection.Timeout%2A> 속성입니다.

trans-unit.source: Thrown when a session is already open on the connection.
trans-unit.target: 세션이 이미 연결에서 열려 있는 경우

trans-unit.source: Thrown when the XML returned from the Server in response to the <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.BeginSession" /> is not well-formed.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.BeginSession" />에 대한 응답으로 서버에서 반환된 XML이 제대로 구성되지 않은 경우

trans-unit.source: Thrown when there is a communications failure with the DSML server or when the server is out of available sessions.
trans-unit.target: DSML 서버와 통신 오류가 있거나 서버에 사용 가능한 세션이 없는 경우

trans-unit.source: An object derived from <see cref="T:System.IAsyncResult" /> that contains state data for this request.
trans-unit.target: 이 요청에 대한 상태 데이터를 포함하는 <see cref="T:System.IAsyncResult" />에서 파생된 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.EndSendRequest(System.IAsyncResult)" /> method completes an asynchronous send request.
A <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlResponseDocument" /> object that contains the results of the request.
Thrown when <paramref name="asyncResult" /> is <see langword="null" />.

Thrown if <paramref name="asyncResult" /> was not returned by the current instance from a call to <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.BeginSendRequest(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument,System.AsyncCallback,System.Object)" />.
trans-unit.target: 현재 인스턴스에서 <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.BeginSendRequest(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument,System.AsyncCallback,System.Object)" />을 호출한 결과 <paramref name="asyncResult" />가 반환되지 않은 경우

trans-unit.source: The request did not complete.
No stream is available.
Thrown when the response returned by server is not valid.
Thrown when abort was previously called or when an error occurred while processing the request.
trans-unit.target: 중단을 이미 호출했거나 요청을 처리하는 동안 오류가 발생한 경우

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.EndSession" /> method ends the session with the DSML server and clears the <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.SessionId" /> property.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.EndSession" /> 메서드는 DSML 서버와의 세션을 종료하고 <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.SessionId" /> 속성을 지웁니다.

trans-unit.source: The method will block while waiting for a response from the DSML server and will time out according to the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryConnection.Timeout%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 메서드가 DSML 서버 로부터 응답을 기다리는 동안 차단 되며에 따라 시간이 초과 됩니다는 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryConnection.Timeout%2A> 속성입니다.

trans-unit.source: If the DSML server has already terminated the session on its own, a <xref:System.Net.WebException> will be thrown.
trans-unit.target: DSML 서버는 자체적으로 세션 이미 종료 되는 <xref:System.Net.WebException> throw 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.SessionId%2A> is still valid after the exception is thrown, the request never reached the server and the connection is still considered valid.
trans-unit.target: 경우는 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.SessionId%2A> 예외가 throw 된, 요청에는 서버에 도달할 수 및 연결이 여전히 유효한 것으로 간주 되 후 여전히 유효 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Thrown when there is a communications failure with the DSML server.
trans-unit.target: DSML 서버와 통신 오류가 있는 경우

trans-unit.source: Thrown when there is no open session.
Sends an object to the DSML server.
A <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryRequest" /> object that contains the request.

The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.SendRequest(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryRequest)" /> method sends a single <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryRequest" /> object.
A <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryResponse" /> object that contains the results of the request.
<paramref name="request" /> is null (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
The DSML server returned an error response.
trans-unit.target: DSML 서버에서 오류 응답을 반환한 경우

trans-unit.source: The operation returned a failure code.
A <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument" /> object sent to the server.

The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.SendRequest(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument)" /> method sends a <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument" /> object to the DSML server.
A <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlResponseDocument" /> object that contains the results of the request.
<paramref name="request" /> is null (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.SessionId" /> property contains the active session ID.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.SessionId" /> 속성에는 활성 세션 ID가 포함되어 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: The active session ID.
The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.SoapActionHeader" /> property contains the SOAP Action Header sent with other HTTP headers.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.SoapActionHeader" /> 속성에는 다른 HTTP 헤더와 함께 보낸 SOAP 작업 헤더가 포함되어 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: The SOAP Action Header sent with other HTTP headers.
trans-unit.target: 다른 HTTP 헤더와 함께 보낸 SOAP 작업 헤더입니다.

trans-unit.source: The default value of this property is "#batchRequest".

The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.Timeout" /> property contains the length of time, in seconds, before the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection" /> times out.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.Timeout" /> 속성에는 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection" /> 시간 제한이 초과되기 전까지의 시간(초)이 포함되어 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: The length of time, in seconds, before the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection" /> times out.
